      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This vehicle is looking for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little elbow grease. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a valuable parts donor. Bring your tools and your vision to bring this one back to life!",
